<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "about_me.JPG", width: 300, alt: "Profile Image", class: 'profile-img' %>

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                  >
                </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <% end %>

        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>This is the thing that I use for unknown purpose,</p>
        <p>  I don't know why, but it can't be useless.</p>
        <p>  Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry's standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged. </p>
        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <!-- <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="education"
          >
            Education
          </button> -->
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              <%= link_to 'VD Company', "https://vd-company.com/" %>
            </div>
            <!-- <div class="card card-block">
              Job2
            </div> -->
          </div>

          <!-- <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Education1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Education2
            </div>
          </div> -->
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
